{"tid":1979033,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★屯門大媽歌舞團轉戰蝴蝶灣 摸手20蚊，摸腰50蚊","createTime":"2020-04-19T06:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T08:55:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9c4a5cbaa495bd142eff023349a2b6b040611626","tid":1979033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4348949/org/afd7ff6fadda7b111f3513340fc53f0e.jpg/HANe7ILM6B1tNQ_e95fg6K-09uhOkbPKh9l6eIfZeng?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4348949%2Forg%2Fafd7ff6fadda7b111f3513340fc53f0e.jpg%2FHANe7ILM6B1tNQ_e95fg6K-09uhOkbPKh9l6eIfZeng%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=dd621774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門蝴蝶灣公園不時有中樂愛好者操曲，他們對突如其來的大媽歌舞團不予置評。曲友劉太表示，原本在蝴蝶灣公園玩音樂的人士絕無賣弄色情，「呢度好正規」，令該處成為音樂愛好者集中地，她坦言擔心屯門公園歪風傳至碼頭一帶：「屯門公園好嘈，好似返咗大陸咁，太密。呢度有海風，希望啲大媽唔好殺到嚟，啲大媽好好手段，會話伯伯你點呀（身體挨着阿伯），我叫我老公新年封10蚊利是，大媽講恭喜發財畀一封，但啲屯門公園阿伯會封幾千蚊。」她直言「啲阿伯好肯畀錢」，但無奈：「啲男人冇地方去好慘，好似我老公咁，𢦀居居坐喺屋企，（覺得）好冇自尊（冇地方去）啲老人家」。<br />\n<br />\n甄紹南表示，據他了解，歌舞大媽表演時有賣弄色情：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「摸手仔20蚊，摸腰50蚊</strong></span></span>，利是放心口都有，單車徑變咗紅燈區咁。」他指歌舞團自2月起在蝴蝶灣公園賣唱，康文署執法將他們趕到單車徑，近日再採取措施以橙色膠網圍封住公園與單車徑之間草坪，阻礙歌迷視線，並會在適當時間進行除草，警方亦會加強巡邏，留意是否有人違反限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/462722/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E6%AD%8C%E8%88%9E%E5%9C%98%E8%BD%89%E6%88%B0%E8%9D%B4%E8%9D%B6%E7%81%A3-%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%9F%E9%81%9412%E6%AA%94%E8%81%9A200%E4%BA%BA-%E9%98%BF%E4%BC%AF%E5%9D%90%E4%BD%8E%E7%AD%89%E7%9D%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F462722%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25BD%2589%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%259D%25B4%25E8%259D%25B6%25E7%2581%25A3-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B3%25B0%25E6%259C%259F%25E9%2581%259412%25E6%25AA%2594%25E8%2581%259A200%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%2598%25BF%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E5%259D%2590%25E4%25BD%258E%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%259D%2587&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=fb8a50ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/462722/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%AA%BD%E6%AD%8C%E8%88%9E%E5%9C%98%E8%BD%89%E6%88%B0%E8%9D%B4%E8%9D%B6%E7%81%A3-%E9%AB%98%E5%B3%B0%E6%9C%9F%E9%81%9412%E6%AA%94%E8%81%9A200%E4%BA%BA-%E9%98%BF%E4%BC%AF%E5%9D%90%E4%BD%8E%E7%AD%89%E7%9D%87</a>"},{"pid":"957586b45fcb2fc5e7408b46da45265715a1c013","tid":1979033,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班大媽有乜資格同唔比屌嘅港女ptgf 並列"},{"pid":"6f41b618151f027d95e4270459d0ece67e422078","tid":1979033,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係恩客"},{"pid":"391773bb94d1959c01d4fc170fb09b454625608f","tid":1979033,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f41b618151f027d95e4270459d0ece67e422078","tid":1979033,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"樓主係恩客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:46:48.000Z","msg":"U?"},{"pid":"18012c2c9db842b3d8053ba321d37baa848ea632","tid":1979033,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"限聚令"},{"pid":"0424fe72a1e4df08136c72995f86a1052a7def10","tid":1979033,"uid":294031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:54:32.000Z","msg":"香港啲ptgf 係比摸唔比屌，<br />\n屯門大媽又係比摸唔比屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9072b2f3fb6830f36fccb138f4ea0aa19fb76453","tid":1979033,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"就咁睇<br />\n明白咩叫：口味隨年紀改變...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as